title: Spyder Auto Installation: 1998-2005 Lexus GS300/GS400 LED Tail Lights
description: This instructional video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder Auto LED tail lights to replace the often-faded tail lights of 1998-2005 Lexus GS300 and GS400 models. These LED tail lights update the look of your Lexus with slick, modern LEDs and offer direct plug and play operation. This tutorial is also peppered with helpful tips throughout to facilitate a successful installation.
tags: Spyder LED Tail Lights, spyder lights, how to install, Lexus GS300, GS 400
